When a WAV file is selected in the FileSystem dock, several import options are available in the Import dock. The set of options available for Ogg Vorbis or MP3 files is different. After importing a sound, it can be played back using AudioStreamPlayer, AudioStreamPlayer2D, or AudioStreamPlayer3D nodes.
